title: Pro Bowl candidates & "Who Says No?"
itunes:title: Pro Bowl candidates & "Who Says No?"
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- discuss their Top 10 under the radar Pro Bowl candidates for this year. They also preview the Chargers vs. Broncos Thursday night matchup and play a new trade game "Who Says No?".

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
